---
title: Chermoula Pork & Veggie Bowl with Garlic Rice & Toasted Almonds
description: This bountiful bowl has "new favourite" written all over it! Our exceptional Chermoula spice blend is the key ingredient, giving adelicious flavour kick to the pork mince. With tender veggies, an aromatic bed of garlic rice and a smattering of toasted almonds to top things off, it's a winner from start to finish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-chermoula-pork-veggie-bowl-671b053b.jpg
